            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E5%88%AB24%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E5%90%83%E9%81%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%9F%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E5%88%AB24%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E5%90%83%E9%81%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%9F%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医生建议别24小时吃遍一座城#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%8C%91%E6%88%9824%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E5%90%83%E9%81%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%9F%8E%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E8%83%B0%E8%85%BA%E7%82%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%8C%91%E6%88%9824%E5%B0%8F%E6%97%B6%E5%90%83%E9%81%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A7%E5%9F%8E%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E8%83%B0%E8%85%BA%E7%82%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#挑战24小时吃遍一座城或致胰腺炎#</span></a>】这个假期，一个名叫"极限24小时吃遍某座城市"的挑战，突然在社交媒体上火热起来：在短时间内，游客进食某一地的各类生猛海鲜、高油高脂、辛辣刺激等食物。医生提醒，这样的饮食状态不可取，食物混杂下肚，极易打乱肠胃消化的"生物钟"，增加消化道负担，引起腹痛、呕吐等症状。“节假日期间因为暴饮暴食，出现急性胰腺炎的发病率也比较高，特别是重度胰腺炎属于高风险的疾病，很容易引起多脏器功能衰竭”。<a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E5%A4%AE%E8%A7%86%E8%B4%A2%E7%BB%8F">@央视财经</a> <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4952351975342108" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视财经的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002sRokily1higqvrybzyj60zk0k0q5v02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/L9WyCImnlx0893sfcTXa01041200vwIx0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1696554192&amp;ssig=mqzeVyQjHT&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Ng5T4pLFlx0893seY3Ta01041200gBd60E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1696554192&amp;ssig=QsXWuRXz2%2F&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/dx4YcPaOlx0893segDbq01041200axUL0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1696554192&amp;ssig=hcPeEzODXM&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4952351975342108" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
